column1: #FORMAT=WebAnno TSV 3.2
#T_SP=webanno.custom.Referent|entity|infstat|salience|identity
#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=Dr. Means ,
#Text=It has come to our attention that you are planning to do abortions at your Harry St. location .
#Text=I am stunned that you would take your career in this direction .

#Text=Fewer people than ever before are pro-abortion , quality physicians would n't even consider associating themselves with it , and more Americans than ever before are unwilling to turn a blind eye to the killing of a baby when the ratio for adoption is 36 couples to 1 baby .
#Text=Maybe you do n't realize the consequences of killing the innocent .
#Text=If Tiller could speak from hell , he would tell you what a soulless existence you are purposefully considering , all in the name of greed .
#Text=Thousands of people are already looking into your background , not just in Wichita , but from all over the U.S.
#Text=They will know your habits and routines .
#Text=They know where you shop , who your friends are , what you drive , where you live .
#Text=You will be checking under your car every day â€” because maybe today is the day someone places an explosive under it .
#Text=People will be picketing your home , your office .
#Text=You will come under greater scrutiny than you 've ever known , legally and professionally .
#Text=Much worse than the disciplinary actions and ethical concerns that you 've been facing .
#Text=You will become a pariah â€” no physician will want to associate with you .
#Text=You will be seen like all the other hacks that have stooped to doing abortions when they were n't good enough to maintain a real practice .
#Text=You will lose your legitimate clientele , as no one bringing a baby into this world wants to be in the same facility where you are also killing them .

#Text=You will have trouble keeping staff who are willing to participate in innocent blood - shedding and wo n't be able to keep the sanitary conditions necessary to maintain a healthy medical facility .
#Text=You will end up having the same kind of rat - infested , dirty facility that they have in north - eastern Kansas .
#Text=Anyone who partners with you will experience the same headaches .
#Text=Not to mention the fact that you will be haunted by bloody , squirming , dismembered babies in your sleep .
#Text=You ca n't do what is morally reprehensible and enjoy peace of mind .
#Text=The Bible says , " There are six things the Lord hates ... hands that shed innocent blood , a heart that devises evil schemes , feet that are quick to rush into evil " Proverbs 6 : 16 - 18 .
#Text=Abortion kills human life - it matters not if you kill it at 6 weeks or at 26 weeks , it 's still the unnatural , violent death of a human baby for the sake of convenience .
#Text=You are doing what the Humane Society would n't allow to happen to a pregnant dog or cat .
#Text=I urge you to think very carefully about the choices you are making .
#Text=There are 3 churches within 1 block of your practice , and many others who must take a stand .
#Text=We will not let this abomination continue without doing everything we can to stop it .
#Text=We pray you will either make the right choice and use your medical practice to heal instead of kill , or that God will bring judgment on you , the likes of which you can not imagine .
#Text=We do n't want you killing our children in our community .
#Text=Good people are tired of this rampant evil , and will stand against you every step of the way .
#Text=Do the world a favor and ABORT this stupid plan of yours .
#Text=It 's not too late to change your mind .
#Text=Angel Dillard
